== a soft builtin error in the bash mood carries a located caret ==
shit: 1:9: error: Builtin 'builtin': 'nosuchbuiltin' is not a shell builtin.
     1 |  builtin nosuchbuiltin
       |          ^~~~~~~~~~~~~ here.
rc=1
== the run keeps going past the soft error ==
shit: 1:9: error: Builtin 'builtin': 'nosuchbuiltin' is not a shell builtin.
     1 |  builtin nosuchbuiltin; echo after
       |          ^~~~~~~~~~~~~ here.
after
== a thrown builtin error in the bash mood is located and soft too ==
shit: 1:6: error: Builtin 'read': Unknown flag '-Z'.
     1 |  read -Z; echo after
       |       ^~ here.
after
